divs: Sighting DetailsWe were on the I4 in orlando going south and looked up and seen a UFO with flashing lights underneath that could not be an airplane or helicopter. It moves in a straight line going our direction bit faster than is. 70 MPH est. We tried to take a picture because it was staying to low to the grown to be a aircraft and knew it was something out of this world because of the awkward lights underneath but couldn't get a straight shot. We finally had to get off our exit and it was gone
Summary: it was flying the same direction as we were lower and slower than an aircraft with flashing lights underit
trends: There have been 112 other sightings in Orlando
